{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb4b1dd4-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s602"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"602"},"text":"§ 602.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reports and examinations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Every national banking association operating foreign branches shall be required to furnish information concerning the condition of such branches to the Comptroller of the Currency upon demand, and every member bank investing in the capital stock of banks or corporations described in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s601"},"text":"section 601 of this title","children":[],"tail":" shall be required to furnish information concerning the condition of such banks or corporations to the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System upon demand, and the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System may order special examinations of the said branches, banks, or corporations at such time or times as it may deem best."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb4b1dd5-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1913-12-23/ch6/s25"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913, ch. 6, § 25","children":[],"tail":" (par.), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/38/273"},"text":"38 Stat. 273","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1916-09-07/ch461"},"text":"Sept. 7, 1916, ch. 461","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/39/755"},"text":"39 Stat. 755","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1919-09-17/ch60/s3"},"text":"Sept. 17, 1919, ch. 60, § 3","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/41/286"},"text":"41 Stat. 286","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1935-08-23/ch614"},"text":"Aug. 23, 1935, ch. 614","children":[],"tail":", title II, § 203(a), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/49/704"},"text":"49 Stat. 704","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb4b1dd6-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb4b1dd7-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"iddb4b1dd8-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of the fourth undesignated par. of section 25 of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1913-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 1913","children":[],"tail":", which comprises this subchapter. For classification of other pars. of section 25 of this Act, see Codification note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s601"},"text":"section 601 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"iddb4b1dd9-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1919—Act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1919-09-17"},"text":"Sept. 17, 1919","children":[],"tail":", substituted “above” for “subparagraph 2 of the first paragraph of this section” in the original, which for purposes of codification appears in text as a reference to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s601"},"text":"section 601 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1916—Act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1916-09-07"},"text":